# Compass — gitignored derived artifacts
#
# Rule: gitignore only pure views derived from other tracked files with no
# user-relevant state of their own. The dashboard fits — it's a regenerated
# HTML view of artifacts that already live in git. Suppressions, refinement
# logs, metrics snapshots, etc. stay tracked because they carry user state.

# Derived dashboard view — regenerated by /dashboard on demand.
docs/dashboard.html

